    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a solid choice for someone looking for a functional driver at a reasonable price. While it remains mechanically sound and drives well for its age, there are visible signs of wear and tear both inside and out. You can expect some minor cosmetic blemishes, such as small scratches or faded paint in certain areas, and the interior shows typical signs of use. It has been regularly serviced, though some minor maintenance tasks may be due soon to keep it running at its best. This is an honest car for anyone who prioritizes utility and value over a showroom appearance.",
